    <item>
      <title>Recovery Moves Index for Van Power: Shore, Drive, or Solar</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/recovery-moves-index/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/recovery-moves-index/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Recovery works best when you choose the best move you can actually execute today.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Start here:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/recovery-window-priority-map/&#34; &gt;Recovery Window Priority Map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/van-power-stability-scorecard/&#34; &gt;Van Power Stability Scorecard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;If you can plug in (shore) -&amp;gt; do this&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;if-you-can-plug-in-shore---do-this&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#if-you-can-plug-in-shore---do-this&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/shore-power-refill-window-plan/&#34; &gt;Shore Power Refill Window Plan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/shore-power-recovery-routine/&#34; &gt;Shore Power Recovery Routine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;If you can drive (but don’t want to add miles) -&amp;gt; do this&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;if-you-can-drive-but-dont-want-to-add-miles---do-this&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#if-you-can-drive-but-dont-want-to-add-miles---do-this&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/drive-recovery-window-plan/&#34; &gt;Drive Recovery Window Plan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/solar-vs-alternator-charging/&#34; &gt;Solar vs Alternator Charging&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;If you’re relying on solar today -&amp;gt; do this&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;if-youre-relying-on-solar-today---do-this&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#if-youre-relying-on-solar-today---do-this&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/solar-capture-window-plan/&#34; &gt;Solar Capture Window Plan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/cloudy-week-power-recovery-plan/&#34; &gt;Cloudy Week Power Recovery Plan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/parking-constraints-van-power-recovery/&#34; &gt;Parking Constraints Van Power Recovery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;If none of these are available this week&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;if-none-of-these-are-available-this-week&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#if-none-of-these-are-available-this-week&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/generator-free-van-power-recovery/&#34; &gt;Generator-Free Van Power Recovery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/quiet-hours-recovery-plan/&#34; &gt;Quiet Hours Recovery Plan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/tier-2-bad-week-protocol/&#34; &gt;Tier 2 Bad Week Protocol&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Next step&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;next-step&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#next-step&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Next step: use the Decision Tree to pick the next best move: &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/van-power-upgrade-decision-tree/&#34; &gt;Van Power Upgrade Decision Tree&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&#xA;If you are shopping, use &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-buyer-guides/&#34; &gt;Fast-Charging Buyer Guides&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/fast-charging-power-station-buyer-checklist/&#34; &gt;Fast-Charging Power Station Buyer Checklist&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, then route to &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations-under-1000/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations Under $1000&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations-for-essentials/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations for Essentials&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations-for-work/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations for Work&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations-for-heat-and-humidity/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations for Heat + Humidity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-fast-charging-power-stations-for-cold-weather/&#34; &gt;Best Fast-Charging Power Stations for Cold Weather&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&#xA;Entry ladder and method routes: &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/best-of/power-stations-under-500/&#34; &gt;Portable Power Stations Under $500&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/under-500-to-tier-2-upgrade-bridge/&#34; &gt;Under-$500 to Tier 2 Upgrade Bridge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/how-we-test-and-source-van-power/&#34; &gt;How We Test and Source Van Power&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&#xA;If you&amp;rsquo;re deciding between solar and fast charging, use this comparison: &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/solar-vs-fast-charging-for-van-life/&#34; &gt;Solar vs Fast Charging for Van Life&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&#xA;For cold weeks with weak solar, use this condition plan: &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/cold-and-cloudy-van-power-recovery/&#34; &gt;Cold + Cloudy Van Power Recovery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Shore Power Recovery Routine for Van Life: A Simple Plug-In Plan That Works</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/shore-power-recovery-routine/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/shore-power-recovery-routine/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Shore Power Recovery Routine for Van Life: A Simple Plug-In Plan That Works&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;shore-power-recovery-routine-for-van-life-a-simple-plug-in-plan-that-works&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#shore-power-recovery-routine-for-van-life-a-simple-plug-in-plan-that-works&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;For many van lifers, shore power is the fastest stability reset available. It gives you predictable recovery when weather and routine become messy. A simple plug-in workflow can reduce power stress without turning every day into battery management.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Shore Power Refill Window Plan: Get a Fast, Respectful Recovery Session</title>
