      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/shore-power-refill-window-plan/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Shore power is often the most reliable recovery move, but only when it is planned on purpose.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Start here:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/shore-power-recovery-routine/&#34; &gt;Shore Power Recovery Routine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/recovery-window-priority-map/&#34; &gt;Recovery Window Priority Map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Step 1 — Choose the right kind of refill window (reality-first)&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;step-1--choose-the-right-kind-of-refill-window-reality-first&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#step-1--choose-the-right-kind-of-refill-window-reality-first&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Examples include campground access, a friend’s driveway, a paid RV spot, or other permitted outlet access.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
